Dole ne Amurka ta ninka yawan kuɗin A.I.
A cewar dan kasuwa kuma mai aikin AI Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki ga Google, Microsoft, da Apple, saboda karfin kasar Sin a fannin fasaha, Amurka ta bukaci ninka yawan kudaden da ta kashe a binciken filin.
Bayanai sun zo ne bayan rassan gwamnatin Amurka daban-daban sun yi tallan AI, duk da cewa ba a da wani shirin AI na Amurka.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta sanar da shirin ta a bara: tana son zama jagora wajen sabunta AI ta 2030.
"Biyan kuɗi na binciken AI sau biyu wuri ne mai kyau don farawa, saboda duk sauran ƙasashe suna da nisa sosai a bayan Amurka, kuma muna neman wani rikici a AI", in ji Lee.
A cewar Lee a wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon, ninka kudaden zai iya kara damar da Amurka za ta samu na gaba mai girma AI juyin juya hali.
Wani littafi da Lee ya rubuta mai taken "AI Superpowers: Shugaba na Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a Face++, daya daga cikin shahararrun masana'antun AI a China, an buga shi "China, Silicon Valley, da New World Order" a wannan watan ta Houghton Mifflin Harcourt.
Ya kirkiro tsarin AI wanda ya rinjayi babban dan wasan Amurka Othello a cikin shekarun 1980s a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon, Daga bisani, ya yi aiki a matsayin mai gudanarwa a Microsoft Research kuma ya zama shugaban sashin China na Google.
