Maimakon haka, an shirya taron da Trump, wanda ke New York don Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, a ranar Alhamis.
Trump ya ce ba ya "son" a kori Rosenstein, amma an dage taron don hana wani rikici da kuma wani binciken da kwamitin shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa ya yi wanda Kavanaugh da daya daga cikin matan da aka zarge shi da cin zarafin jima'i, Dr Christine Blasey Ford , suka shaida.
A ranar Juma'a, Trump ya ba da umarnin a gudanar da bincike na mako guda na FBI game da Kavanaugh, wanda ya kara jinkirta zaben Majalisar Dattijai gaba daya.
Sarah Sanders, sakataren Trump, ta yi magana da Fox News a ranar Lahadi.
