Masu sayen gidaje na kasashen waje za su fuskanci babban nauyin da ake zargi da yin sayayya a Birtaniya, tare da karin kudade don taimakawa marasa gida, Theresa May ta ce a yau.
Wannan matakin zai zama wani yunkuri na rage nasarar kokarin Jeremy Corbyn na jawo hankalin matasa ta hanyar yin alkawarin gidaje masu araha da kuma samun kudin shiga.
Ƙara harajin hatimi zai ba wa mutane da kamfanoni masu biyan haraji a cikin Burtaniya, tare da sauran bangarorin kuɗi don tallafawa ƙoƙarin gwamnati na yaki da rashin barci.
