Tsunami da girgizar ƙasa a Indonesia
Jami'an da ke kula da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da ta afku a birnin Palu, Indonesia, a ranar Jumma'a sun ce aƙalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu, kuma ana sa ran adadin mutanen da suka mutu zai ƙaru.
Ma'aikatan agaji ba su iya samun bayanai daga gundumar Donggala ba, wanda ke arewacin Palu kuma yana kusa da tsakiyar girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.5.
Bayan wannan rikici, fiye da mutane 16,000 suka bar birnin.
Ga wasu abubuwa masu ban sha'awa game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu ita ce babban birnin yankin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, wanda ke kan gajeren bay a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, kuma yana da yawan mutane 379,800 kamar yadda aka kiyasta a shekara ta 2017.
Sa'ad da girgizar ƙasa da ambaliyar ƙasa suka auku, birnin ya yi bikin cika shekara 40.
Donggala wani yanki ne na arewa maso yammacin Sulawesi wanda ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 mil) na bakin teku.
A shekara ta 2017, gundumar, wadda ke ƙarƙashin gundumar gundumar, tana da yawan mutane 299,200.
Fishing da noma sune tushen tattalin arzikin yankin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, musamman a lardin Donggala.
Ana kuma yin hakar nikki a cikin lardin, ko da yake yana da yawa a Morowali, a gefen Sulawesi.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, an yi ambaliyar ruwa a birnin Palu da Donggala sau da yawa, in ji Hukumar Kula da Al'amuran Gaggawa ta ƙasar Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, ambaliyar ruwa ta yi a birnin Donggala kuma ta kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ta lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje.
A shekara ta 1996, ambaliyar ruwa ta yi wa yankin Donggala na yamma da ta kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana kan babbar hanyar Pacific Ring of Fire kuma tana fama da girgizar ƙasa sau da yawa.
Waɗannan su ne wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da ambaliyar ruwa da suka faru a kwanan nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afku a yammacin yankin Aceh a arewacin Sumatra, Indonesia, kuma ta yi ambaliyar ruwa da ta shafi ƙasashe 14, ta kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen watan Maris da kuma farkon watan Afrilu, girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani ta yi ta girgiza yankin yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, da ke gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 6.8 ta afkawa kudu da Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da mummunan raunin da ya shafi kudu, inda kusan mutane 700 suka mutu.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai da ke gabar Sumatra, kuma ta jawo raƙuman ruwa mai tsawon mita 10 da suka lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma suka kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai zurfi ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya na Aceh, ta haifar da tashin hankali da damuwa yayin da mazauna ƙasar suka tuna da lalacewar da girgizar ƙasa da ambaliyar ruwa ta haifar a shekara ta 2004.
Ko da yake babu wani tashin hankali a wannan lokacin, mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a cikin gine-ginen.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda mutane sama da 500 suka mutu, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
